<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.ir_usage_item">
<b>ir_usage_item</b> selects the items an <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.information_usage_right"/> can be applied to.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: applied_usage_right  
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.applied_usage_right"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.applied_usage_right">
An <b>applied_usage_right</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="activity:mim:Activity_mim.applied_action_assignment"/>
 is the link from an <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.information_usage_right"/> which forms the items it applies to.
<note>The link runs through the <express_ref linkend="activity:mim:Activity_mim.applied_action_assignment"/>

 through an <express_ref linkend="action_schema:ir_express:action_schema.action"/>

 to the
<express_ref linkend="action_schema:ir_express:action_schema.action_method"/> that implements the right.</note>
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: applied_usage_right  Attribute: items 
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.applied_usage_right.items"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.applied_usage_right.items">
the set of data that the usage right applies to.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: information_right  
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.information_right"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.information_right">
An <b>information_right</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="action_schema:ir_express:action_schema.action_method"/> used to represent an information right.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: information_usage_right  
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.information_usage_right"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.information_usage_right">
An <b>information_usage_right</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="action_schema:ir_express:action_schema.action_method"/> used to represent  the usage in a particular context of an information right.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: right_to_usage_association  
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.right_to_usage_association"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.right_to_usage_association">
A <b>right_to_usage_association</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="action_schema:ir_express:action_schema.action_method_relationship"/> which provides the link between an information right and its usage.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: right_to_usage_association  Attribute: right_applied 
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.right_to_usage_association.right_applied"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.right_to_usage_association.right_applied">
the right that is to be applied in the given context.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: right_to_usage_association  Attribute: right_usage 
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.right_to_usage_association.right_usage"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.right_to_usage_association.right_usage">
the context in which the right is applied.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: usage_association  
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.usage_association"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.usage_association">
A <b>usage_association</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="action_schema:ir_express:action_schema.action_method_relationship"/> which relates a pair of <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.information_usage_right">information_usage_rights</express_ref>.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: usage_association  Attribute: related 
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.usage_association.related"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.usage_association.related">
one of the instances of <express_ref
linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.information_usage_right"/>
participating in the relationship. If one element of the relationship is dependent upon the other, this attribute shall be the dependent one.
</ext_description>


<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Information_rights_mim  Entity: usage_association  Attribute: relating 
   <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.usage_association.relating"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_mim.usage_association.relating">
the other instance of <express_ref linkend="information_rights:mim:Information_rights_mim.information_usage_right">information_usage_rights</express_ref> participating in the relationship. 
</ext_description>


